<p>Most live trading algorithms run on co-located servers racked in <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="https://www.equinix.com/data-centers/americas-colocation/united-states-colocation/new-york-data-centers/ny7">Equinix</a>. Co-location reduces several factors that can interfere with your algorithm, including downtime from internet outages, equipment repairs, and natural disasters.</p>